Property name="LABELS" value="Trigger Parameters:Trigger Parameters:Threshold:0:0:V:REAL::1:The <b>Threshold</b> (<b>T</b>) of the POP Trigger input. To determine the actual threshold (<b>TL</b> and <b>TH</b>) substitute <b>Threshold</b> (<b>T</b>) and <b>Hysteresis</b> (<b>H</b>) in each of the following formulas\\:<table><tr><td><nobr><u>Input Logic Level</u></nobr></td><td><u>Actual Threshold</u></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td><nobr><b>Threshold</b> + 0.5 * <b>Hysteresis</b></nobr></td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td><b>Threshold</b> - 0.5 * <b>Hysteresis</b></td></tr></table><img src=\"\\:/threshold_hysteresis.png\">,Output Parameters:Output Parameters:Output low voltage:1:0:V:REAL::1:The low voltage of the output pin.,Output Parameters:Output Parameters:Output high voltage:0:0:V:REAL::1:The high voltage of the output pin.,Trigger Parameters:Trigger Parameters:Hysteresis:1:0:V:REAL:1p:1:The <b>Hysteresis</b> (<b>H</b>) of the POP Trigger input. To determine the actual threshold (<b>TL</b> and <b>TH</b>) substitute <b>Threshold</b> (<b>T</b>) and <b>Hysteresis</b> (<b>H</b>) in each of the following formulas\\:<table><tr><td><nobr><u>Input Logic Level</u></nobr></td><td><u>Actual Threshold</u></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td><nobr><b>Threshold</b> + 0.5 * <b>Hysteresis</b></nobr></td></tr><tr><td>0</td><td><b>Threshold</b> - 0.5 * <b>Hysteresis</b></td></tr></table><img src=\"\\:/threshold_hysteresis.png\">,::Divide by two?::::GROUPCHECK:::,Trigger Parameters:Divide by two?:Initial condition:1:0::LIST:0|1::The initial condition of the output when <b>Divide by two?</b> is checked.,Trigger Parameters:Trigger Parameters:Propagation delay:2:0:s:REAL:0:1:The propagation delay of the POP Trigger Schematic Device.,Trigger Parameters:Divide by two?:Trigger condition:0:0::LIST:0_TO_1|1_TO_0::Determines the triggering condition of the input pin\\:<br /><ul><li><b>0_TO_1</b> for rising edge triggered</li><li><nobr><b>1_TO_0</b> for falling edge triggered</nobr></li></ul>" autopos=1 normal=Bottom rotated=Left protected=1 visible=0 font=Default order=-1
